**PARTIES PRESENT:**

* **SUMMIT LEAD:** Dir. Calvin Bold;[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]Chosen as the **SUMMIT LEAD** due to their critical involvement in the initial deactivation of LOTUS.[[/span]]
* Ryoto Hishakaku;
* Dir. Yves Isabi;
* Dir. Vandis Kelvin;
* Lord Angus Le Moix;
